title: The Folk Implosion Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents The Folk Implosion performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 1, 2025.

00:46 Moonlit Kind
05:05 Walk Thru Me
09:18 The Day You Died
14:29 My Little Lamb
18:02 Natural One
 
Lou Barlow - Bass, Vocals
John Davis - Guitar, Electronics, Drums, Vocals

Host: Troy Nelson
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht
